de.axnsoftware.settings

Interface IBackingStore

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PropertiesBackingStoreImpl

    public interface IBackingStore
    The interface IBackingStore models a wrapper for a backing store which is responsible for both loading and storing configuration data.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Carsten Klein "cklein"

      • getProperties

        Object getProperties()
                     throws BackingStoreException
        Returns a copy of the loaded properties. This will throw an IllegalStateException if the properties have not been loaded.
        Returns:
        the properties
        Throws:
        BackingStoreException

      • deleteProperties

        void deleteProperties()
                      throws BackingStoreException
        Deletes the properties. Depending on the implementation this could mean that the file will be removed from the file system, or that the entries in a registry will be removed.
        Throws:
        BackingStoreException
